definitions.definition: A flammable liquid consisting of a mixture of refined petroleum hydrocarbons , mainly used as a motor fuel ; petrol .
examples: You can't put gasoline in this car. This car takes diesel fuel.

definitions.definition: Any specific kind of this fuel.
examples: He was trying to invent a cleaner-burning gasoline .
The refinery produces a wide range of gasolines .

definitions.definition: Marijuana , especially very potent or of high quality.
An alcoholic beverage made of vodka and energy drink.

main_definition: ( uncountable , Canada , US ) A flammable liquid consisting of a mixture of refined petroleum hydrocarbons , mainly used as a motor fuel ; petrol .
